front_matter:
  id: pm-11t5
  title: Harden recursive test-all detection for pnpm dlx and npm exec launchers
  description: Reject linked test commands that invoke pm test-all through pnpm dlx/npm exec package launcher forms and keep runtime skip parity.
  type: Task
  status: closed
  priority: 1
  tags[6]: "area:test-command",code,"milestone:3",pm-cli,"priority:1",tests
  created_at: "2026-03-05T11:05:52.887Z"
  updated_at: "2026-03-05T11:30:19.133Z"
  deadline: "2026-03-06T23:59:00.000Z"
  author: cursor-maintainer
  estimated_minutes: 90
  acceptance_criteria: pm test --add rejects recursive test-all commands launched via pnpm dlx and npm exec package-spec forms; pm test --run skips legacy recursive entries for those forms; docs and tests reflect behavior; coverage remains 100 percent.
