body: "Context: recursive test-all guard currently catches pm/node/npx launcher forms but allows pnpm dlx pm-cli@latest --json test-all. Approach: docs-first contract update, then token-aware launcher parsing for pnpm dlx and npm exec variants, plus regression tests for add-time rejection and runtime skip behavior."
